Recon 2.2: from reconstruction to model of human metabolism.

Swainston N(1), Smallbone K(2), Hefzi H(3), Dobson PD(2), Brewer J(4), Hanscho 
M(5), Zielinski DC(6), Ang KS(7), Gardiner NJ(8), Gutierrez JM(3), Kyriakopoulos 
