Systems Biology Program, University of California, San Diego, La Jolla, CA USA.
(13)Austrian Centre of Industrial Biotechnology, Vienna, Austria.
(14)Manchester Centre for Synthetic Biology of Fine and Speciality Chemicals 
(SYNBIOCHEM), Manchester Institute of Biotechnology, The University of 
